1
00:01:24,516 --> 00:01:30,368
<i>[Weaving A Tale of Love 2]</i>

2
00:01:32,132 --> 00:01:35,360
<i>[Episode 5]</i>

3
00:01:36,115 --> 00:01:38,115
In order to prepare sacrificial offerings
for Lady Lu,

4
00:01:38,115 --> 00:01:39,755
lady has been hard at work
for such a long time,

5
00:01:39,755 --> 00:01:42,655
embroidering her favorite scenes,
stitch by stitch,

6
00:01:42,655 --> 00:01:44,755
How could you possibly
understand these feelings?

7
00:01:44,755 --> 00:01:47,315
Do you think the lady is hiding
because she's afraid of you?

8
00:01:47,955 --> 00:01:49,024
What a joke!

9
00:01:56,595 --> 00:01:59,935
Yunu, you mention the late madam every day,

10
00:01:59,935 --> 00:02:02,115
But you've never even been to her grave,
have you?

11
00:02:04,315 --> 00:02:06,895
Today I will take you with me,

12
00:02:06,895 --> 00:02:09,155
So you can pay your respects

13
00:02:09,155 --> 00:02:10,635
and kowtow at the grave of Sister Lu,

14
00:02:40,675 --> 00:02:43,955
Liuli, so this is the place

15
00:02:44,955 --> 00:02:46,016
you wanted to come with me,

16
00:02:53,195 --> 00:02:54,595
Sister Lu is a person I deeply respect,

17
00:02:55,515 --> 00:02:57,355
<i>[Tomb of First Wife Lady Lu Qi]</i>
I've long wanted to visit her grave and pay my respects,

18
00:02:59,755 --> 00:03:02,395
Shouyue, I am not a petty person,

19
00:03:03,115 --> 00:03:04,395
Sister Lu passed away many years ago,

20
00:03:04,995 --> 00:03:06,915
but you still
have affection and righteousness for her,

21
00:03:06,915 --> 00:03:08,635
You're the husband I like,

22
00:03:10,115 --> 00:03:11,795
If you miss Sister Lu in the future,

23
00:03:12,475 --> 00:03:14,635
let's come and see her together, alright?

24
00:03:19,155 --> 00:03:20,795
Sister Lu was forced by the Princess Linhai

25
00:03:20,795 --> 00:03:22,075
and your clan to death,

26
00:03:23,155 --> 00:03:25,715
But she had grievances she couldn't express
and revenge she couldn't take,

27
00:03:25,715 --> 00:03:27,035
The most hateful thing is

28
00:03:28,475 --> 00:03:30,035
that Sister Lu has already been dead
for many years,

29
00:03:30,795 --> 00:03:31,875
Princess Linhai

30
00:03:31,875 --> 00:03:34,715
still claims to have a deep mother-daughter
relationship with Sister Lu,

31
00:03:35,635 --> 00:03:38,155
continuing to frame and exploit you,

32
00:03:41,915 --> 00:03:45,395
Sister Lu, I know you were aggrieved

33
00:03:45,995 --> 00:03:47,008
and reluctant when you were dead,

34
00:03:48,115 --> 00:03:51,195
If you are aware in the afterlife,
please bless me and Shouyue,

35
00:03:51,755 --> 00:03:53,515
blessing us to avenge you soon,

36
00:03:57,315 --> 00:04:00,955
Over a decade ago, I married Qi
under my mother's orders,

37
00:04:02,195 --> 00:04:03,200
After my wedding,

38
00:04:03,835 --> 00:04:05,655
the Hedong Duke's family can only
keep their promise

39
00:04:05,655 --> 00:04:07,955
to return the Pei family estate,
which they've managed for years, back to me,

40
00:04:08,915 --> 00:04:10,715
But at that time,
I had just taken General Su as my mentor,

41
00:04:11,555 --> 00:04:13,675
so, I entrusted the management of
the family property to Lady Qi,

42
00:04:15,035 --> 00:04:18,015
Unbeknownst to me, the Princess Royal
had employed tactics at the manor,

43
00:04:18,015 --> 00:04:19,136
resulting in significant losses,

44
00:04:19,955 --> 00:04:23,175
Without telling me, Lady Qi used
the entire dowry to cover the losses,

45
00:04:23,175 --> 00:04:24,195
but it was still not enough,

46
00:04:25,355 --> 00:04:26,955
The people of the Pei family joined forces,

47
00:04:26,955 --> 00:04:29,155
forcing Qi and her unborn child to death,

48
00:04:30,115 --> 00:04:32,235
Princess took advantage of the situation
to reclaim the family property,

49
00:04:34,195 --> 00:04:35,675
<i>[Tomb of First Wife Lady Lu Qi]</i>
I failed to protect them,

50
00:04:36,435 --> 00:04:38,115
It is the greatest pain of my life,

51
00:05:10,555 --> 00:05:12,995
Yunu, do you still remember that

52
00:05:12,995 --> 00:05:14,235
I'll take back your belongings?

53
00:05:17,075 --> 00:05:18,115
You forgot so quickly?

54
00:05:28,075 --> 00:05:29,675
<i>Could it be the indenture of sale
she's talking about</i>

55
00:05:41,835 --> 00:05:43,875
A few days ago,
while carrying out official duties,

56
00:05:44,395 --> 00:05:45,675
I found this in the thieves' den,

57
00:05:49,220 --> 00:05:50,240
<i>[Slave Purchase Agreement]</i>

58
00:06:09,995 --> 00:06:12,795
There's a matter in which I need to
make use of your dexterity,

59
00:06:18,180 --> 00:06:24,288
<i>[Slave Purchase Agreement]</i>

60
00:06:28,315 --> 00:06:29,755
The Residence of the Hedong Duke
had reported a crime,

61
00:06:30,555 --> 00:06:31,755
They said thieves had struck the yard,

62
00:06:32,355 --> 00:06:35,275
<i>[Gold and Jade Fill the Hall]</i>
Among the stolen items is Yunu's slave purchase agreement,

63
00:06:36,235 --> 00:06:38,395
A few days ago,
I led some people to capture a big thief,

64
00:06:38,915 --> 00:06:40,275
The thief has escaped from the den,

65
00:06:40,955 --> 00:06:42,155
Nothing else was left behind,

66
00:06:42,955 --> 00:06:44,515
Only this slavery purchase contract
was left behind,

67
00:06:45,355 --> 00:06:48,835
This slavery purchase contract
cannot be compared to gold and silver,

68
00:06:48,835 --> 00:06:51,995
There's no use if the thief steals it,

69
00:06:52,635 --> 00:06:55,815
It's also possible
that the thief intentionally abandoned it,

70
00:06:55,815 --> 00:06:56,864
You're right,

71
00:06:59,395 --> 00:07:00,395
<i>How is this possible?</i>

72
00:07:00,955 --> 00:07:02,995
<i>My indenture of sale
was in the hands of the elder princess,</i>

73
00:07:06,315 --> 00:07:08,435
Even if the case is not solved,
you can still recover the loot,

74
00:07:09,435 --> 00:07:11,875
Shouyue, you have good methods,

75
00:07:13,355 --> 00:07:14,432
Just a fluke,

76
00:07:15,635 --> 00:07:17,355
Thanks to the blessings of the eldest princess,

77
00:07:21,875 --> 00:07:25,175
I told Shouyue about indenture of sale of Yunu,

78
00:07:25,175 --> 00:07:27,955
you were originally going to be given to us,

79
00:07:27,955 --> 00:07:29,775
Now that we have found it back,

80
00:07:29,775 --> 00:07:32,775
It would be enough to send someone
to give a report to the eldest princess,

81
00:07:32,775 --> 00:07:35,215
Yet Shouyue insists on being meticulous,

82
00:07:35,215 --> 00:07:36,675
He thinks that indenture of sale of Yunu

83
00:07:36,675 --> 00:07:38,835
was lost by royal princess,

84
00:07:38,835 --> 00:07:40,615
so it must be returned to royal princess,

85
00:07:40,615 --> 00:07:42,995
Then, it should be handed over to us
by the royal princess,

86
00:07:42,995 --> 00:07:44,555
Only then can it be considered
proper etiquette,

87
00:07:52,315 --> 00:07:53,376
Cui,

88
00:07:55,235 --> 00:07:56,435
Hand it to Lady Liuli,

89
00:08:00,675 --> 00:08:01,760
Yes,

90
00:08:06,595 --> 00:08:07,648
Yes,

91
00:08:12,395 --> 00:08:14,555
And thank you, Princess,

92
00:08:20,915 --> 00:08:23,035
There are two pieces of jewelry in this box,

93
00:08:24,275 --> 00:08:28,035
We have been master and servant,
These are for you to remember,

94
00:08:30,195 --> 00:08:31,595
Thank you for the grace, Princess,

95
00:08:32,235 --> 00:08:33,755
Take good care of yourself in the future,

96
00:08:35,075 --> 00:08:36,675
Don't forget, no matter where you go,

97
00:08:37,595 --> 00:08:40,755
you are a person
from my Residence of the Hedong Duke,

98
00:08:41,715 --> 00:08:45,515
Yes, Yunu will remember,

99
00:09:06,848 --> 00:09:07,904
Please calm your anger,

100
00:09:08,475 --> 00:09:11,255
Pei Shouyue and Kudi Liuli

101
00:09:11,255 --> 00:09:13,715
held a counterfeit agreement,

102
00:09:13,715 --> 00:09:15,456
The real one is indeed in my hand,

103
00:09:15,456 --> 00:09:17,156
But I have no way to refute,

104
00:09:18,475 --> 00:09:20,235
And I can't take out the real one,

105
00:09:20,235 --> 00:09:21,995
I can only let them talk nonsense,

106
00:09:21,995 --> 00:09:23,195
It really pisses me off,

107
00:09:24,555 --> 00:09:25,755
Madam, calm down,

108
00:09:26,555 --> 00:09:29,195
Pei Shouyue and Kudi Liuli
are really too cunning,

109
00:09:29,755 --> 00:09:32,715
But who could have imagined that Pei Shouyue,

110
00:09:32,715 --> 00:09:35,635
as an imperial court official,
dared to openly forge documents,

111
00:09:36,595 --> 00:09:38,875
He's audacious in the extreme,

112
00:09:43,395 --> 00:09:45,475
It has always been me scheming against others,

113
00:09:46,115 --> 00:09:48,355
But carelessly, I ended up being the one
schemed against,

114
00:09:49,155 --> 00:09:50,795
I will absolutely not forgive them,

115
00:09:52,315 --> 00:09:54,595
Please calm your anger, The future is long,

116
00:10:03,355 --> 00:10:05,635
Go,

117
00:10:06,212 --> 00:10:08,484
<i>[Bei Meng House]</i>

118
00:10:10,275 --> 00:10:13,875
Go,

119
00:10:16,555 --> 00:10:19,315
Shouyue, thank you,

120
00:10:21,675 --> 00:10:24,715
I really didn't expect you
to come up with this method

121
00:10:24,715 --> 00:10:26,395
making the arrogant eldest princess

122
00:10:27,435 --> 00:10:29,115
end up swallowing a bitter pill in silence,

123
00:10:30,635 --> 00:10:33,475
The bitterness and resentment accumulating
in my heart for many years

124
00:10:33,995 --> 00:10:35,155
have also been healed quite a bit,

125
00:10:35,915 --> 00:10:38,395
We are husband and wife,
there's no need for thanks,

126
00:10:40,035 --> 00:10:42,635
It is said that the hardest thing
between husband and wife

127
00:10:42,635 --> 00:10:44,475
is all about sharing weal and woe together,

128
00:10:45,315 --> 00:10:48,755
But I've never worried about these things
between us,

129
00:10:50,355 --> 00:10:55,475
You know, my only fear is
that you don't believe in me,

130
00:10:57,515 --> 00:10:59,235
When I first saw Yunu,

131
00:11:00,515 --> 00:11:01,632
I was scared to death,

132
00:11:02,355 --> 00:11:04,355
I was afraid
you'd fall for the Princess's schemes,

133
00:11:05,755 --> 00:11:06,995
doubting my love for you,

134
00:11:08,835 --> 00:11:11,155
That time Yunu came to the county office
while you were away,

135
00:11:12,515 --> 00:11:15,695
I knew then that
Princess wanted to use her old tricks again,

136
00:11:15,695 --> 00:11:17,995
My Lord,
please drink this bowl of ginger soup first,

137
00:11:18,755 --> 00:11:21,275
Afterwards, Yunu will assist you
in changing clothes,

138
00:11:21,955 --> 00:11:25,275
Her attempt to divide us is to
disregard all means for the property,

139
00:11:27,155 --> 00:11:29,435
Don't you understand what I'm saying?
Hurry up and get out,

140
00:11:32,795 --> 00:11:34,595
Cheng, take her out,

141
00:11:34,595 --> 00:11:35,616
Yes,

142
00:11:37,028 --> 00:11:38,944
<i>[Qing Feng Pavilion]</i>

143
00:11:39,915 --> 00:11:41,615
Just now, I've asked someone
to prepare hot soup,

144
00:11:41,615 --> 00:11:43,355
Have a soak to ward off the cold,

145
00:11:44,715 --> 00:11:47,275
But I didn't bring a change of clothes,
what should we do?

146
00:11:52,355 --> 00:11:54,035
Why are you still here?

147
00:11:58,995 --> 00:12:00,955
My lord, you refuse to eat the food and drink
brought by Yunu,

148
00:12:01,635 --> 00:12:04,995
I'm afraid you also don't want to
wear the clothes brought by Yunu,

149
00:12:09,115 --> 00:12:11,275
Aren't these the clothes made
by the lady herself for my lord?

150
00:12:12,315 --> 00:12:14,435
My lord merely refuses to eat the meals
you bring,

151
00:12:15,115 --> 00:12:16,755
But these clothes made by the lady herself

152
00:12:16,755 --> 00:12:18,355
are my lord's beloved possessions,

153
00:12:33,435 --> 00:12:34,695
I never would have thought that

154
00:12:34,695 --> 00:12:36,355
Yunu would have tampered with the clothes,

155
00:12:36,955 --> 00:12:38,275
You discovered it the next day,

156
00:12:38,995 --> 00:12:41,536
How can Cheng's little lies escape you?

157
00:12:41,536 --> 00:12:42,715
My lady,

158
00:12:42,715 --> 00:12:46,675
Shouyue, how did you change clothes
before you had bathed?

159
00:12:48,235 --> 00:12:50,275
Madam, it was Cheng's oversight,

160
00:12:50,275 --> 00:12:51,995
I earlier unintentionally spilled tea on

161
00:12:51,995 --> 00:12:53,475
the Master's clothes,

162
00:12:53,475 --> 00:12:55,895
Hence, Cheng changed a set of clothes
for the Master,

163
00:12:55,895 --> 00:12:57,275
What did I tell you before?

164
00:12:58,995 --> 00:13:00,315
Did you just let my words

165
00:13:00,315 --> 00:13:01,835
go in one ear and out the other?

166
00:13:01,835 --> 00:13:04,275
Hurry up and explain to your lady clearly
what exactly is going on,

167
00:13:04,955 --> 00:13:05,984
I'm sorry,

168
00:13:06,955 --> 00:13:09,795
Master told me that
if the lady asks about this matter,

169
00:13:09,795 --> 00:13:12,475
he must tell all without concealment,

170
00:13:12,475 --> 00:13:13,515
And he must not deceive,

171
00:13:14,555 --> 00:13:16,095
Cheng is indeed loyal to you,

172
00:13:16,095 --> 00:13:18,075
Please, madam, calm your anger,

173
00:13:18,075 --> 00:13:20,935
I feared you might misunderstand your husband,
so I deliberately hid the truth,

174
00:13:20,935 --> 00:13:22,415
It was Cheng
who took it upon himself to decide,

175
00:13:22,415 --> 00:13:24,435
Then you put on the act of being angry

176
00:13:24,995 --> 00:13:26,155
for Yunu outside to see,

177
00:13:28,435 --> 00:13:29,440
But thank you,

178
00:13:31,555 --> 00:13:33,195
Thank you for believing in me
without any hesitation,

179
00:13:34,435 --> 00:13:38,395
Who just said there's no need for 'thank you'
between husband and wife?

180
00:13:40,115 --> 00:13:42,575
I trust you,

181
00:13:42,575 --> 00:13:44,355
But you never fully trusted me,

182
00:13:44,875 --> 00:13:48,480
Otherwise, why would you want to
hide so many things from me?

183
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:49,515
I didn't want to see you

184
00:13:49,515 --> 00:13:50,915
suffer the slightest harm,

185
00:13:54,835 --> 00:13:57,835
You are right, I was in the wrong,

186
00:13:59,195 --> 00:14:01,315
I apologize to you,
It won't happen again next time,

187
00:14:03,875 --> 00:14:04,875
If that's the case,

188
00:14:05,595 --> 00:14:08,835
then I'll take full responsibility
for Yunu's matters in the future,

189
00:14:08,835 --> 00:14:10,355
Don't take it to heart,

190
00:14:11,275 --> 00:14:12,315
I'm hardly heartbroken,

191
00:14:32,915 --> 00:14:34,675
My lady, Yunu has arrived,

192
00:14:39,435 --> 00:14:41,595
Yunu pays respects to my lady and master,

193
00:14:42,195 --> 00:14:44,915
May I inquire why my lady has summoned Yunu?

194
00:14:45,875 --> 00:14:49,515
Yunu, you still remember
what I told you before, right?

195
00:14:50,755 --> 00:14:52,895
Now I hold your indenture of sale,

196
00:14:52,895 --> 00:14:54,755
As long as
you remain well-behaved in the future,

197
00:14:55,675 --> 00:14:58,595
the promise I made to you before still holds,

198
00:14:59,995 --> 00:15:03,435
In two years' time,
I will find you a good family to marry into,

199
00:15:03,995 --> 00:15:05,315
Do you understand my meaning?

200
00:15:08,435 --> 00:15:11,155
You may go back and rest now,

201
00:15:21,955 --> 00:15:24,275
My lady, the bath is ready,

202
00:15:24,275 --> 00:15:25,315
Please proceed to the bath,

203
00:15:26,875 --> 00:15:28,995
My lady, didn't you promise Lady Yu

204
00:15:28,995 --> 00:15:30,875
that you would send her new clothes today?

205
00:15:30,875 --> 00:15:33,675
Oh yes, how could I have forgotten that?

206
00:15:34,315 --> 00:15:37,395
It's still time to make a trip
to the general's mansion before the curfew,

207
00:15:37,955 --> 00:15:41,475
But my lady, the bath will be cold
by the time you return,

208
00:15:41,995 --> 00:15:45,075
The matter of bathing is small,
but I can't let the mother-in-law wait in vain,

209
00:15:45,915 --> 00:15:47,935
The bath is ready, Shouyue,

210
00:15:47,935 --> 00:15:50,595
Can you take a bath first while I am out?

211
00:15:51,835 --> 00:15:54,275
You just go ahead, I will do as you said,

212
00:15:59,044 --> 00:16:02,016
<i>[Pei Mansion]</i>

213
00:16:07,140 --> 00:16:09,760
<i>[Compose Poetry]</i>

214
00:16:25,732 --> 00:16:27,200
<i>[Compose Poetry]</i>

215
00:16:50,235 --> 00:16:51,755
What are you afraid of?

216
00:16:52,835 --> 00:16:54,195
The lady has gone out,

217
00:16:54,715 --> 00:16:56,875
Naturally, he won't be able to return
in a short while,

218
00:16:58,075 --> 00:16:59,595
Newlyweds,

219
00:16:59,595 --> 00:17:03,355
The lady left you alone for a bath,
isn't it lonely?

220
00:17:10,355 --> 00:17:14,035
Yunu knows
that you can't forget your first wife,

221
00:17:14,915 --> 00:17:19,235
Why don't you pretend
I'm your first wife tonight

222
00:17:20,235 --> 00:17:21,755
to soothe your nostalgia?

223
00:17:28,035 --> 00:17:29,056
Why are you?

224
00:17:34,555 --> 00:17:37,275
You unrepentant thing,
Why aren't you kneeling down?

225
00:17:48,635 --> 00:17:50,995
I once disguised myself as a man
in the palace for ten years,

226
00:17:50,995 --> 00:17:53,235
Even His Majesty and Lady Wu

227
00:17:53,235 --> 00:17:54,555
could not see through my male disguise,

228
00:17:54,555 --> 00:17:58,275
What's more, you were just drawing a screen,

229
00:18:00,595 --> 00:18:04,435
Yunu, considering that you are being coerced
by the princess,

230
00:18:04,435 --> 00:18:06,755
I tried to get back your indenture of sale,

231
00:18:07,355 --> 00:18:08,675
and gave you another chance,

232
00:18:09,435 --> 00:18:11,275
But you did not know how to cherish it

233
00:18:11,275 --> 00:18:13,835
but kept going your own way
and did not know to repent,

234
00:18:14,675 --> 00:18:16,395
I, as the mistress, have to

235
00:18:16,395 --> 00:18:17,715
show no mercy this time,

236
00:18:20,835 --> 00:18:21,995
I am still very curious,

237
00:18:23,355 --> 00:18:24,955
Inside the box given to you by the Princess,

238
00:18:24,955 --> 00:18:26,195
what exactly is the treasure inside?

239
00:18:26,715 --> 00:18:29,275
You'll risk your life for it

240
00:18:29,275 --> 00:18:30,955
and challenge my bottom line again,

241
00:18:34,035 --> 00:18:36,315
My lady, I found this in the

242
00:18:36,315 --> 00:18:38,835
secret compartment of the wooden box
given to Yunu by the princess,

243
00:18:39,395 --> 00:18:40,480
Half of a land deed,

244
00:18:43,364 --> 00:18:45,824
<i>[Deed of Farmland]</i>

245
00:18:46,515 --> 00:18:48,075
This piece of land is truly not small

246
00:18:48,955 --> 00:18:50,835
The Princess has only given you half of it,

247
00:18:50,835 --> 00:18:53,995
She promised to give you the other half
after your task is complete, isn't it?

248
00:18:53,995 --> 00:18:55,595
Lady, your guess is spot on,

249
00:18:57,635 --> 00:18:58,915
But what can you do to me?

250
00:19:00,115 --> 00:19:03,275
Although I'm a servant,
I was given by the Princess,

251
00:19:04,315 --> 00:19:05,875
The Princess made it clear from the start that

252
00:19:06,435 --> 00:19:09,155
you're not allowed to sell, beat,

253
00:19:09,155 --> 00:19:10,515
scold, or abuse me,

254
00:19:11,035 --> 00:19:12,615
Otherwise,
it would be considered insubordination

255
00:19:12,615 --> 00:19:13,955
and against the goodwill of elders,

256
00:19:18,715 --> 00:19:23,195
Indeed, there are not many methods
I can use on you,

257
00:19:23,795 --> 00:19:26,995
You can't be sold, beaten, scolded, nor abused,

258
00:19:29,915 --> 00:19:31,835
But you are so likable in appearance,

259
00:19:33,835 --> 00:19:37,475
If I were to bring you into the palace
to present you to Lady Wu,

260
00:19:38,115 --> 00:19:39,435
Lady Wu would surely like you,

261
00:19:40,235 --> 00:19:42,035
Considering Lady Wu's status and position,

262
00:19:42,915 --> 00:19:46,055
