that Princess Linhai gave me,

263
00:19:46,055 --> 00:19:49,355
If she asks for it,
there is absolutely nothing wrong,

264
00:19:49,875 --> 00:19:53,275
This way, I wouldn't offend the Princess,
and it wouldn't be unfair to you,

265
00:19:54,035 --> 00:19:56,395
Don't you think so?

266
00:19:57,115 --> 00:19:58,235
You want to send me to the palace?

267
00:20:01,875 --> 00:20:04,955
Once you're in the palace, I'll ask sister Wu

268
00:20:06,835 --> 00:20:09,115
to transfer you to the Forensic Bureau,

269
00:20:09,835 --> 00:20:12,035
My grandfather is in charge of
the Forensic Bureau in the palace,

270
00:20:12,675 --> 00:20:15,355
I will definitely ask him
to take good care of you,

271
00:20:15,955 --> 00:20:16,992
The Forensic Bureau？

272
00:20:19,595 --> 00:20:20,715
What is the Forensic Bureau?

273
00:20:22,195 --> 00:20:23,795
Haven't you heard of the Forensic Bureau?

274
00:20:25,115 --> 00:20:27,635
The Forensic Bureau is the place inside the palace
where funeral affairs are handled,

275
00:20:28,275 --> 00:20:31,035
There, one only deals with the deceased,

276
00:20:31,835 --> 00:20:34,515
From now on, you will be dealing with those
who have died from old age or disease,

277
00:20:35,275 --> 00:20:39,755
Tell me,
is this arrangement considerate enough for you?

278
00:20:41,115 --> 00:20:43,795
Spare my life, My lady!

279
00:20:43,795 --> 00:20:46,195
It was all Yunu's fault before,
please spare me, My lady!

280
00:20:46,995 --> 00:20:49,275
I won't do it again, Please, mercy,

281
00:20:49,955 --> 00:20:51,355
I gave you a chance before,

282
00:20:51,355 --> 00:20:53,715
It was you who were greedy for
wealth and glory,

283
00:20:55,875 --> 00:20:58,715
My lady, please set me free,

284
00:20:59,675 --> 00:21:00,795
If you would let me go,

285
00:21:01,555 --> 00:21:04,315
I swear that I will never appear
in Chang'an City again,

286
00:21:06,235 --> 00:21:09,315
Let you go free? This matter is controlled
by the laws of our country,

287
00:21:09,315 --> 00:21:11,035
