because I want to,

288
00:21:12,235 --> 00:21:13,395
My lady, there are things you don't know,

289
00:21:18,315 --> 00:21:19,755
I was originally a respectable family child,

290
00:21:20,395 --> 00:21:23,155
Although in Pingkang Fang,
I was carefully nurtured by my stepmother,

291
00:21:23,155 --> 00:21:25,155
