I somewhat resemble the late first wife,

294
00:21:30,595 --> 00:21:32,435
Hence, she forcibly bought me to be a servant,

295
00:21:33,715 --> 00:21:35,435
My lady, please believe me this time,

296
00:21:39,555 --> 00:21:40,835
My lady, if you agree to release me,

297
00:21:41,915 --> 00:21:43,995
Yunu naturally has a way
to return to being a good citizen,

298
00:21:44,755 --> 00:21:47,015
Residence of the Hedong Duke bought me,

299
00:21:47,015 --> 00:21:48,975
Therefore, the matter of
changing the slave status

300
00:21:48,975 --> 00:21:50,635
absolutely won't involve you, my lady,

301
00:21:51,475 --> 00:21:52,595
Please, mercy,

302
00:21:56,715 --> 00:22:00,915
Ni, let Cheng go to the yamen for a trip,

303
00:22:01,555 --> 00:22:03,355
Just say we only came to know today

304
00:22:03,355 --> 00:22:06,355
that Yunu was originally a good citizen,
please let them check it out,

305
00:22:06,875 --> 00:22:07,936
If there is no mistake,

306
00:22:09,475 --> 00:22:10,955
please cancel her lowly status,

307
00:22:38,755 --> 00:22:41,995
My lady, I am eternally grateful
and have no way to repay your kindness,

308
00:22:42,835 --> 00:22:46,155
Please, my lady,
do take good care of your health,

309
00:22:49,315 --> 00:22:50,555
If Yunu does not die,

310
00:22:52,035 --> 00:22:54,755
I will surely make a grass knot or champ a ring

311
00:22:57,635 --> 00:22:58,688
in order to repay kindness,

312
00:23:07,635 --> 00:23:11,355
Yunu, if you sincerely repent,

313
00:23:12,675 --> 00:23:13,995
that would be enough to do right by me,

314
00:24:11,835 --> 00:24:13,515
Cheng has found a new residence,

315
00:24:14,155 --> 00:24:15,675
Let's move there together next month,

316
00:24:16,395 --> 00:24:17,472
Why move?

317
00:24:27,515 --> 00:24:28,835
I really like this home,

318
00:24:29,955 --> 00:24:31,275
Can we not move?

319
00:24:53,795 --> 00:24:56,435
So this is the clever person you picked for me?

320
00:24:56,435 --> 00:24:57,675
She is worse than rubbish,

321
00:24:58,315 --> 00:25:00,515
I hope she would sow discord
between the Shouyue couple,

322
00:25:00,515 --> 00:25:03,415
It cost me so much money and thought,

323
00:25:03,415 --> 00:25:06,835
As a result, Yunu went to the county office
to ask for her release,

324
00:25:06,835 --> 00:25:09,475
Pei Xingjian directly stamped and approved it,

325
00:25:14,915 --> 00:25:16,995
How many more years can I live?

326
00:25:18,115 --> 00:25:19,955
I have racked my brains so much,

327
00:25:21,395 --> 00:25:22,875
With so much preparation,

328
00:25:23,435 --> 00:25:25,835
isn't it all
because I'm worrying about your future?

329
00:25:28,195 --> 00:25:29,715
- I'm incapable,
- I'm incapable

330
00:25:29,715 --> 00:25:31,275
- I was wrong,
- I was wrong,

331
00:25:34,395 --> 00:25:38,675
If you make mistakes in the future,
you must accept the punishment

332
00:25:39,915 --> 00:25:43,435
Don't blame me for not warning you beforehand,

333
00:25:44,075 --> 00:25:45,152
Yes,

334
00:26:33,155 --> 00:26:35,115
My lady, this dough has been leaven so well,

335
00:27:16,555 --> 00:27:17,824
Why are you cooking again?

336
00:27:18,435 --> 00:27:19,968
Didn't I tell you

337
00:27:19,968 --> 00:27:22,055
I forbade you from working
so hard day and night like this?

338
00:27:22,055 --> 00:27:23,155
Why don't you listen?

339
00:27:24,035 --> 00:27:27,195
Making soup for you is my favorite thing to do,
How could it be laborious?

340
00:27:35,035 --> 00:27:36,096
Here you go,

341
00:27:41,435 --> 00:27:43,955
Today, the princess Linhai

342
00:27:43,955 --> 00:27:45,955
brought all the property deeds from Luoyang,

343
00:27:46,675 --> 00:27:48,355
I have no idea
what bad idea they are concocting now,

344
00:27:49,995 --> 00:27:51,040
What are your thoughts on this?

345
00:27:51,675 --> 00:27:54,115
This Luoyang family's property is
a thorn in the side of the Pei Family,

346
00:27:54,875 --> 00:27:56,635
It's also a piece of meat
in the mouth of the princess,

347
00:27:57,475 --> 00:27:59,295
If it always remains in our hands,

348
00:27:59,295 --> 00:28:01,355
then our struggle with the princess

349
00:28:01,355 --> 00:28:02,475
will be endless,

350
00:28:03,555 --> 00:28:05,595
It really has become a hot potato,

351
00:28:06,115 --> 00:28:09,795
So unless this family property is owned
by someone

352
00:28:10,355 --> 00:28:13,355
that Princess can't offend,
the matter can be finished,

353
00:28:14,835 --> 00:28:16,515
That slave Yunu was freed by me,

354
00:28:17,315 --> 00:28:18,435
Does it bring you great pain to leave her?

355
00:28:22,675 --> 00:28:23,776
What do you think?

356
00:28:25,755 --> 00:28:27,075
My wife is astute and capable,

357
00:28:27,075 --> 00:28:28,475
How could she fall for someone else's schemes?

358
00:28:29,675 --> 00:28:33,195
Liuli, I've made up my mind
about the family property in Luoyang,

359
00:28:34,635 --> 00:28:37,675
I've written a document for you,

360
00:28:38,475 --> 00:28:41,675
I entrust the document to you for your use,

361
00:28:43,195 --> 00:28:46,955
Rest assured, I will never sit back
and let anyone bully me,

362
00:28:46,955 --> 00:28:49,995
I will protect myself and our home,

363
00:29:11,395 --> 00:29:14,755
What a great post!
How come I've never seen this post before?

364
00:29:16,515 --> 00:29:18,635
Your calligraphy,
though not as good as your painting,

365
00:29:19,195 --> 00:29:20,755
but your judgment is quite sharp,

366
00:29:22,075 --> 00:29:23,875
Take a look, whose handwriting is this?

367
00:29:24,755 --> 00:29:28,615
The cursive script flows with a rhythmic grace,
The strokes are bold and unconstrained,

368
00:29:28,615 --> 00:29:30,195
Truly the style of a master,

369
00:29:32,035 --> 00:29:35,335
But I just can't make out
whose handwriting this is,

370
00:29:35,335 --> 00:29:36,995
This is the authentic work of Zhang Boying,

371
00:29:37,555 --> 00:29:38,875
The authentic work of Zhang Boying?

372
00:29:41,475 --> 00:29:42,795
This is truly a rarity,

373
00:29:43,315 --> 00:29:46,395
