Zhang Boying's authentic works, but to no avail,

375
00:29:52,515 --> 00:29:54,355
Zhang Boying's authentic works
are indeed very rare,

376
00:29:56,035 --> 00:30:00,055
Despite all my efforts,
I have only seen four or five pieces,

377
00:30:00,055 --> 00:30:01,555
That was all due to rare good fortune,

378
00:30:02,075 --> 00:30:03,995
Today, Chu Suiliang found me,

379
00:30:04,835 --> 00:30:06,475
He let me identify this calligraphy piece,

380
00:30:08,555 --> 00:30:12,955
But look at this calligraphy, this paper
and this aura,

381
00:30:13,515 --> 00:30:14,635
It can't be counterfeited,

382
00:30:15,595 --> 00:30:17,395
Even if it were
among Zhang Boying's authentic works,

383
00:30:17,955 --> 00:30:19,040
it is considered top notch,

384
00:30:19,595 --> 00:30:23,155
If it's an authentic piece,
why did Chu Suiliang let you take it home?

385
00:30:23,835 --> 00:30:24,975
Your husband's writing,

386
00:30:24,975 --> 00:30:26,955
in Chang'an city, is somewhat famous,

387
00:30:28,595 --> 00:30:30,435
Chu Suiliang brought the calligraphy piece
to me,

388
00:30:30,995 --> 00:30:32,995
Of course, he wants me to help him by copying,

389
00:30:34,835 --> 00:30:36,315
Yesterday, I went to visit my foster mother,

390
00:30:37,355 --> 00:30:41,155
My foster mother said
that His Majesty intends to depose Queen Wang,

391
00:30:41,155 --> 00:30:44,315
To replace her with Empress Lady Wu,
is this matter true?

392
00:30:46,795 --> 00:30:49,475
Exactly, led by
Chu Suiliang and Chancellor Zhangsun,

393
00:30:49,475 --> 00:30:51,275
