at the forefront are vehemently against it,

394
00:30:51,795 --> 00:30:53,795
It seems His Majesty has no choice,

395
00:30:54,675 --> 00:30:56,875
But a lot of effort has been made
both openly and behind the scenes,

396
00:30:57,675 --> 00:31:01,195
This time, the emperor
has made a firm decision,

397
00:31:02,475 --> 00:31:03,835
His Majesty has been enthroned for many years,

398
00:31:04,435 --> 00:31:06,755
But he is still controlled by the ministers
in the court everywhere,

399
00:31:09,035 --> 00:31:10,995
You are the emperor's intimate minister,

400
00:31:10,995 --> 00:31:13,235
His Majesty wants to make Lady Wu his queen,

401
00:31:13,755 --> 00:31:16,475
Depending on your and my relationship
with His Majesty and Lady Wu,

402
00:31:16,475 --> 00:31:19,635
everyone is convinced that
you will advocate for the deposal of the queen

403
00:31:19,635 --> 00:31:21,635
to help Lady Wu ascend the throne,

404
00:31:22,435 --> 00:31:24,915
But Chu Suiliang and Chancellor Zhangsun
are on the same side,

405
00:31:24,915 --> 00:31:28,395
In theory, they will guard against you,

406
00:31:29,315 --> 00:31:30,336
You're overthinking it,

407
00:31:30,336 --> 00:31:32,635
I will return this calligraphy copybook
sooner or later,

408
00:31:32,635 --> 00:31:34,635
Should we return it to him tomorrow?

409
00:31:36,475 --> 00:31:38,115
No need to rush to return it,

410
00:31:38,115 --> 00:31:40,435
In the next few days,
I want to seriously copy it several times,

411
00:31:50,115 --> 00:31:52,075
Nice,

412
00:31:56,435 --> 00:31:57,915
This is the summer harvest
