414
00:31:59,575 --> 00:32:00,835
So much!

415
00:32:00,835 --> 00:32:02,975
<i>[Pei]</i>
Look, So much!

416
00:32:02,975 --> 00:32:04,235
What a huge industry this must be!

417
00:32:24,555 --> 00:32:28,032
Ni, where is the outfit I made
for my mother-in-law?

418
00:32:28,032 --> 00:32:29,075
Remember to bring it,

