for her generosity and integrity,

431
00:32:59,415 --> 00:33:01,375
Words fly from mouth to mouth quickly,

432
00:33:01,375 --> 00:33:03,015
I'm afraid it won't even take half a day,

433
00:33:03,015 --> 00:33:06,035
The relatives of Pei
should have heard the news,

434
00:33:06,555 --> 00:33:09,755
The day before yesterday,
Lady Lu sent a message from the princess,

435
00:33:09,755 --> 00:33:14,115
She will hold a banquet the day after tomorrow
