the day after tomorrow,

440
00:33:26,035 --> 00:33:27,595
It's impressive how clearly you see,

441
00:33:28,915 --> 00:33:31,835
If so, respectful obedience is the best course,

442
00:33:31,835 --> 00:33:35,795
Tan, tell them that I have already left,

443
00:33:35,795 --> 00:33:37,095
I went to General Su's residence,

444
00:33:37,095 --> 00:33:39,035
Tell them to just leave the things here,

445
00:33:40,155 --> 00:33:41,184
Yes,

446
00:33:42,155 --> 00:33:45,595
Wait a moment,
tell Gu to prepare the car at the back door,

447
00:33:45,595 --> 00:33:46,656
I'll leave from the back door,

